1
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:46,780
=Auspicious Nobles=

2
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:49,940
=Episode 14=

3
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:52,500
(It's Official!
Tower Master & Crown Prince's Scandal)

4
00:00:53,060 --> 00:00:55,420
(Inspectorate)

5
00:00:55,430 --> 00:00:55,990
Your Highness.

6
00:00:56,390 --> 00:00:57,520
(Uphold the Law with Justice)
I have already bought

7
00:00:57,520 --> 00:00:58,960
every recent issue
of the Wangshi Chronicle.

8
00:01:03,350 --> 00:01:06,120
"When autumn comes
on the eighth of September,

9
00:01:06,950 --> 00:01:09,870
my flowers will bloom,
and all others will wither.

10
00:01:10,640 --> 00:01:13,430
Their soaring fragrance
will pierce Chang'an,

11
00:01:14,760 --> 00:01:19,280
and the city will be clad
in golden armor."

12
00:01:23,070 --> 00:01:24,070
Good.

13
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:27,560
What a murderous intent.

14
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:29,640
What grand ambition.

15
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:37,510
"How can I bow and scrape
to serve the powerful,

16
00:01:38,070 --> 00:01:39,760
and deny myself a joyful smile?"

17
00:01:40,070 --> 00:01:42,480
Refusing to bow to the powerful?

18
00:01:43,480 --> 00:01:46,280
Who is the most powerful person
in Great Yong?

19
00:01:55,540 --> 00:01:57,420
(Autumn Meditations, Poem 4)

20
00:01:58,230 --> 00:02:00,430
"The mansions of princes and nobles

21
00:02:01,510 --> 00:02:03,640
all have new masters."

22
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:09,310
New masters...

23
00:02:12,310 --> 00:02:13,400
I think

24
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:17,520
she wants to be
the new master of Great Yong!

25
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:19,630
Yuanhe,

26
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:21,360
you are taking things out of context.

27
00:02:22,310 --> 00:02:22,910
Father,

28
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:25,360
the Tower Master's poetry
is bold and unbridled,

29
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:26,680
but she has no such intent.

30
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:28,380
Even if she doesn't
have such intent now,

31
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:29,430
what about the future?

32
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:31,750
The people of Great Yong

33
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:35,150
are all idolizing her
preferences and behavior.

34
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:37,150
If she is a rebel,

35
00:02:38,310 --> 00:02:39,120
Great Yong

36
00:02:40,430 --> 00:02:41,680
will be in grave danger.

37
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:45,030
Father, the Tower Master won't...

38
00:02:45,030 --> 00:02:45,520
Enough.

39
00:02:51,190 --> 00:02:52,000
Yuanzhao,

40
00:02:53,180 --> 00:02:55,710
you are simple-minded and were used
by the Wangshi Tower Master.

41
00:02:56,430 --> 00:02:58,120
I will not pursue it this time.

42
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:00,030
But starting today,

43
00:03:00,630 --> 00:03:03,750
the imperial business affairs
are handed over to the Crown Prince.

44
00:03:05,430 --> 00:03:07,280
Stay in the palace
and reflect on your actions.

45
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:08,870
Yuanhe,

46
00:03:10,430 --> 00:03:11,240
pass down my decree.

47
00:03:11,520 --> 00:03:13,520
The Wangshi Tower Master
is misleading the public.

48
00:03:13,630 --> 00:03:14,710
Arrest her now,

49
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:16,360
dead or alive.

50
00:03:16,710 --> 00:03:20,870
All businesses under her name
will be dealt with by the Crown Prince.

51
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:23,120
I shall obey the decree.

52
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:25,870
By order of the Crown Prince,

53
00:03:25,870 --> 00:03:27,630
burn down all
of the Wangshi Tower Master's bases

54
00:03:27,630 --> 00:03:28,840
- and confiscate all assets!
- What are you doing?

55
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:30,030
- Freeze!
- Let go of me!

56
00:03:33,190 --> 00:03:34,680
My money!

57
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:36,910
The money I worked so hard
to earn is still inside!

58
00:03:36,910 --> 00:03:37,430
Are you crazy?

59
00:03:37,430 --> 00:03:38,240
My treasures.

60
00:03:38,430 --> 00:03:39,870
Let go.

61
00:03:39,870 --> 00:03:40,430
Let go of me.

62
00:03:40,430 --> 00:03:41,630
Hang in there, Tower Master.

63
00:03:41,710 --> 00:03:43,430
Where there is life, there is hope.

64
00:03:43,430 --> 00:03:44,310
Hope, my foot!

65
00:03:44,310 --> 00:03:45,660
It's all burned to ashes this time.

66
00:03:46,150 --> 00:03:47,910
Zheng Yuanhe, you scoundrel.

67
00:03:47,910 --> 00:03:48,710
Wordplay, huh?

68
00:03:48,720 --> 00:03:49,960
I am going to stab you to death!

69
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:51,150
Stab you to death!

70
00:03:51,150 --> 00:03:53,960
Stab you to death, you dog.

71
00:03:54,870 --> 00:03:57,150
I will kill you...

72
00:03:58,080 --> 00:03:58,870
Tower Master.

73
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:00,630
Come on, hurry up.

74
00:04:03,380 --> 00:04:05,060
(Uphold the Law with Justice)

75
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:07,270
Your Highness, we searched
the Second Prince's residence,

76
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:08,990
but there is no sign
of the Wangshi Tower Master.

77
00:04:09,150 --> 00:04:10,030
She escaped again.

78
00:04:13,110 --> 00:04:14,520
But we discovered this secret letter

79
00:04:14,530 --> 00:04:16,400
that wasn't
completely destroyed by the fire.

80
00:04:20,950 --> 00:04:22,510
(Wangshi Secret Workshop)
A mysterious place was mentioned inside.

81
00:04:22,750 --> 00:04:25,360
It seems Wangshi Tower
has a secret workshop.

82
00:04:26,270 --> 00:04:27,240
Investigate further.

83
00:04:27,870 --> 00:04:29,160
Dig three feet into the ground

84
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:33,720
to uncover all of her hideouts for me.

85
00:04:34,520 --> 00:04:35,290
Yes, Your Highness.

86
00:04:36,620 --> 00:04:38,020
(Wangshi Secret Workshop)

87
00:04:38,020 --> 00:04:39,940
(Pan Residence)

88
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:43,190
The gang of bandits are monsters.

89
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:45,160
They locked me up in a dark

90
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:47,430
and damp mountain cave.

91
00:04:47,430 --> 00:04:48,630
They didn't give me any food

92
00:04:48,870 --> 00:04:50,120
and made me work.

93
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,950
They made me clean the stables

94
00:04:51,950 --> 00:04:53,270
and chop firewood.

95
00:04:53,270 --> 00:04:54,750
Hurry up and sit down.

96
00:04:55,160 --> 00:04:56,430
Look at my hands.

97
00:04:56,830 --> 00:04:58,190
They are all blistered.

98
00:04:59,070 --> 00:05:01,240
I am an official
of the imperial court after all.

99
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:02,680
For them to treat me like this...

100
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:03,830
This is going too far!

101
00:05:09,630 --> 00:05:10,720
What is it now?

102
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:14,480
Qingqing used this opportunity

103
00:05:14,870 --> 00:05:16,070
to take all my jewelry

104
00:05:16,510 --> 00:05:18,120
and keep it for herself.

105
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:20,510
What?

106
00:05:20,510 --> 00:05:21,340
("Hard it is to meet,
and as hard to part.)

107
00:05:21,340 --> 00:05:22,660
(The east wind is weak,
and the flowers wither.")

108
00:05:31,070 --> 00:05:32,920
Tower Master, please take your medicine.

109
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:34,630
I'm busy. I'll drink it later.

110
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,900
("Hard it is to meet,
and as hard to part.)

111
00:05:46,900 --> 00:05:48,280
(The east wind is weak,
and the flowers wither.")

112
00:05:49,310 --> 00:05:52,310
Tower Master, the fever
must have addled your brain.

113
00:05:52,510 --> 00:05:55,950
Why are you drawing
love paintings of Zheng Yuanhe?

114
00:05:56,310 --> 00:05:56,680
And...

115
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:59,120
And writing love poems to him?

116
00:06:00,630 --> 00:06:01,600
Tell me,

117
00:06:02,070 --> 00:06:03,870
if a rebel leader

118
00:06:03,870 --> 00:06:06,360
doesn't hate the Crown Prince
who captured her,

119
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:08,480
but instead shows him humble devotion,

120
00:06:08,830 --> 00:06:09,720
what will people think?

121
00:06:11,870 --> 00:06:14,750
They'll either think
the Crown Prince is so charming

122
00:06:14,760 --> 00:06:16,120
that he can captivate his enemies,

123
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:19,040
or else...

124
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:23,680
He has been colluding with you all along.

125
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:27,160
I get it now.

126
00:06:27,560 --> 00:06:28,270
Tower Master,

127
00:06:28,430 --> 00:06:30,680
you want the Emperor
to suspect the Crown Prince.

128
00:06:31,070 --> 00:06:31,720
Exactly.

129
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:34,270
The Emperor is paranoid.

130
00:06:34,430 --> 00:06:37,480
The more Zheng Yuanhe
tries to deny any connection to me,

131
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:39,160
the more guilty he will look.

132
00:06:40,630 --> 00:06:41,720
When Jiuzhu arrives,

133
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:44,870
tell him to make mass copies
of these poems and paintings

134
00:06:44,870 --> 00:06:47,750
and distribute them
all over the scholars' teahouses.

135
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:49,830
Understood, Tower Master.

136
00:06:52,190 --> 00:06:54,070
Only by keeping this jerk

137
00:06:54,630 --> 00:06:56,830
trapped in his manor
and unable to come out

138
00:06:57,160 --> 00:06:59,000
can I focus on making money.

139
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:02,390
Zheng Yuanhe,

140
00:07:02,830 --> 00:07:05,120
just wait, I'm going to disgust you!

141
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:07,830
Tower Master.

142
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:13,270
Still sleeping?

143
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:14,920
Look what time it is.

144
00:07:15,430 --> 00:07:16,920
You're really a lazy glutton.

145
00:07:19,070 --> 00:07:19,830
Pan Yang,

146
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:21,680
I'm in a bad mood today.

147
00:07:21,700 --> 00:07:22,750
Get straight to the point.

148
00:07:22,750 --> 00:07:23,630
Otherwise, get out.

149
00:07:24,070 --> 00:07:24,680
You jerk.

150
00:07:24,870 --> 00:07:25,680
How dare you...

151
00:07:31,190 --> 00:07:31,950
Qingqing,

152
00:07:32,190 --> 00:07:34,310
you must have
been working too hard lately.

153
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:36,000
You should get plenty of rest.

154
00:07:36,070 --> 00:07:38,120
I'll have some supplements sent over.

155
00:07:39,310 --> 00:07:41,310
What a wolf in sheep's clothing, huh?

156
00:07:41,510 --> 00:07:43,160
What wicked scheme are you plotting now?

157
00:07:43,510 --> 00:07:45,630
You've misunderstood me.

158
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:47,560
Since you're unwell,

159
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:49,760
someone has to look after
the family businesses, right?

160
00:07:50,310 --> 00:07:52,480
Yang is currently
highly favored by the Crown Prince.

161
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,830
He needs to work even harder
at such a critical moment.

162
00:07:57,310 --> 00:07:58,160
Qingqing,

163
00:07:58,870 --> 00:08:01,240
why don't you just sign this agreement,

164
00:08:01,570 --> 00:08:03,630
and I'll temporarily manage
the businesses for you?

165
00:08:08,830 --> 00:08:10,680
I am just sick,

166
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:12,950
not about to die.

167
00:08:13,210 --> 00:08:16,120
Every single thing you wear and eat
was paid for with the money I earned.

168
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:17,970
What do these businesses
have to do with you?

169
00:08:18,070 --> 00:08:19,120
Get out of here!

170
00:08:19,630 --> 00:08:21,040
Don't push your luck.

171
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:23,950
(Agreement)
You are going to sign this today,

172
00:08:24,430 --> 00:08:25,920
or I'll kill you.

173
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,390
What are you doing?

174
00:08:28,390 --> 00:08:29,390
Let go.

175
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:30,630
Let go of me...

176
00:08:33,510 --> 00:08:34,360
Let go!

177
00:08:37,510 --> 00:08:38,150
Yang.

178
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:16,790
Who are you?

179
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:17,970
Should I kill them?

180
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:28,480
You want to steal my businesses?

181
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:29,910
No...

182
00:09:29,910 --> 00:09:31,270
It's not stealing.

183
00:09:31,270 --> 00:09:32,750
We're family.

184
00:09:32,800 --> 00:09:34,030
I just wanted to help you out...

185
00:09:34,030 --> 00:09:35,080
Li Muyan,

186
00:09:35,630 --> 00:09:38,630
even if I signed
this transfer agreement today,

187
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:41,320
there is no way you
could ever take over these businesses.

188
00:09:42,510 --> 00:09:44,600
I don't have the energy
for your petty games now.

189
00:09:44,870 --> 00:09:46,320
I'm going to show you

190
00:09:47,030 --> 00:09:49,030
whether these businesses depend on me

191
00:09:49,550 --> 00:09:51,320
or on a few worthless pieces of paper.

192
00:09:58,080 --> 00:09:59,750
The Wangs, the Bais, the Wus, the Zhaos,

193
00:09:59,870 --> 00:10:01,080
and all these shopkeepers...

194
00:10:01,510 --> 00:10:04,200
When did our family business
gain such massive influence?

195
00:10:05,360 --> 00:10:08,000
I am the Crown Prince's
favorite general now.

196
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:10,000
Why would I fear these merchants?

197
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:11,910
Today,

198
00:10:12,270 --> 00:10:14,030
I will make sure you replace Li Qingqing

199
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:16,480
and take over all of her businesses.

200
00:10:20,670 --> 00:10:21,840
She's here.

201
00:10:27,270 --> 00:10:28,240
- Ms. Li.
- Ms. Li.

202
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:29,750
Why have we been called

203
00:10:29,750 --> 00:10:30,960
here today?

204
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:35,840
Li Muyan wants
to take charge of my businesses

205
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:37,630
(Agreement)
and partner with you all.

206
00:10:38,080 --> 00:10:39,630
I wonder what you all think about this.

207
00:10:41,510 --> 00:10:42,480
That won't do.

208
00:10:42,870 --> 00:10:44,270
We only answer to you, Ms. Li.

209
00:10:44,860 --> 00:10:46,030
If the business changes hands,

210
00:10:46,270 --> 00:10:48,270
we might as well forget
about this partnership.

211
00:10:48,270 --> 00:10:48,910
- Indeed.
- Exactly.

212
00:10:48,910 --> 00:10:51,030
Mr. Bai, I also know how to do business,

213
00:10:51,150 --> 00:10:52,510
and I'm no worse than Li Qingqing.

214
00:10:52,510 --> 00:10:54,270
With me protecting you,

215
00:10:54,510 --> 00:10:55,790
I won't let you lose out.

216
00:10:56,070 --> 00:10:58,030
You're just a drill master
who trains soldiers,

217
00:10:58,200 --> 00:11:00,000
yet you call yourself a general all day.

218
00:11:00,270 --> 00:11:01,480
Aren't you embarrassed?

219
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:02,120
What did you say?

220
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:02,720
Exactly.

221
00:11:02,720 --> 00:11:04,870
Everyone knows you
act like a dog all day

222
00:11:04,870 --> 00:11:06,630
just to flatter the Crown Prince, no?

223
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:08,270
That's right.

224
00:11:08,510 --> 00:11:10,270
The commerce of Great Yong

225
00:11:10,270 --> 00:11:11,960
is managed by the Second Prince.

226
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:15,440
Even the Crown Prince
doesn't have the right to interfere.

227
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:17,630
Traitors! You're all traitors.

228
00:11:18,630 --> 00:11:20,320
I'll report this to
the Crown Prince now,

229
00:11:20,870 --> 00:11:22,960
and have all
your traitorous heads chopped off.

230
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:26,360
You have quite
the official authority, Pan Yang.

231
00:11:26,670 --> 00:11:30,080
Why don't you take
my head along with theirs?

232
00:11:30,440 --> 00:11:31,440
Greetings, Your Highness.

233
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:33,190
- Greetings, Your Highness.
- Greetings, Your Highness.

234
00:11:33,720 --> 00:11:34,960
Greetings, Your Highness.

235
00:11:40,630 --> 00:11:41,670
No, Your Highness...

236
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:43,320
These people

237
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:45,550
are using their wealth
to steal my family's business.

238
00:11:45,550 --> 00:11:46,720
Your business?

239
00:11:47,870 --> 00:11:50,670
That belongs to Lady Qingqing and me.

240
00:11:51,550 --> 00:11:53,240
What?

241
00:12:00,110 --> 00:12:03,470
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

242
00:12:04,230 --> 00:12:07,630
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

243
00:12:08,390 --> 00:12:10,150
♪Your smile♪

244
00:12:10,390 --> 00:12:12,670
♪Melts away the winter snow♪

245
00:12:12,670 --> 00:12:16,350
♪One fleeting glance says more
than a thousand words♪

246
00:12:16,830 --> 00:12:20,150
♪Yet I stand before you♪

247
00:12:20,870 --> 00:12:24,710
♪Unable to recognize your eyes♪

248
00:12:25,110 --> 00:12:27,030
♪Though fate tries♪

249
00:12:27,030 --> 00:12:29,630
♪To make us pass each other by♪

250
00:12:29,830 --> 00:12:33,270
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

251
00:12:33,510 --> 00:12:35,150
♪Though time slips by♪

252
00:12:35,150 --> 00:12:36,910
♪As day turns into night♪

253
00:12:37,430 --> 00:12:41,470
♪I still remember
our days at Wangshi Tower♪

254
00:12:41,870 --> 00:12:44,270
♪One glance at you lasts a lifetime♪

255
00:12:44,270 --> 00:12:46,030
♪Blessed by fate♪

256
00:12:46,030 --> 00:12:51,190
♪I believe this moment
will last forever♪

257
00:12:51,190 --> 00:12:53,630
♪Your smiling face♪

258
00:12:53,630 --> 00:12:56,470
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

259
00:12:56,470 --> 00:13:00,110
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

260
00:13:00,630 --> 00:13:04,070
♪And wander the world together♪

261
00:13:04,070 --> 00:13:05,430
♪Holding you close♪

262
00:13:05,430 --> 00:13:07,950
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

263
00:13:07,950 --> 00:13:10,270
♪Your tenderness♪

264
00:13:10,270 --> 00:13:13,150
♪Is the brightest moon♪

265
00:13:13,150 --> 00:13:16,830
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

266
00:13:17,350 --> 00:13:20,670
♪Our love will never fade away♪

267
00:13:20,670 --> 00:13:23,110
♪Though heaven and earth grow old♪

268
00:13:23,630 --> 00:13:27,910
♪My heart will remain forever pure♪

269
00:13:37,390 --> 00:13:39,550
♪Your smiling face♪

270
00:13:39,710 --> 00:13:42,310
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

271
00:13:42,630 --> 00:13:46,470
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

272
00:13:46,710 --> 00:13:50,190
♪And wander the world together♪

273
00:13:50,190 --> 00:13:51,510
♪Holding you close♪

274
00:13:51,510 --> 00:13:54,150
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

275
00:13:54,150 --> 00:13:56,430
♪Your tenderness♪

276
00:13:56,430 --> 00:13:59,270
♪Is the brightest moon♪

277
00:13:59,270 --> 00:14:03,030
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

278
00:14:03,470 --> 00:14:06,830
♪Our love will never fade away♪

279
00:14:06,830 --> 00:14:09,470
♪Though heaven and earth grow old♪

280
00:14:09,750 --> 00:14:13,870
♪My heart will remain forever pure♪
